{"tid":1838612,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 大家有咩旅遊景點會一去再去?","createTime":"2020-01-24T05:46:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T13:06:25.000Z","uid":45645,"like":0,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"249314889d3ea4385c00feee6d422583613d0e7a","tid":1838612,"uid":45645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:46:58.000Z","msg":"即係如果你再一次去同一個國家或者地區旅行，你點都會PLAN再去一次既地方<br />\n<br />\n咁我就去過唔算多國家，但以下係我自己去過兩次或以上既地方<br />\n<br />\n亞洲︰<br />\n<br />\n日本 - 東京廸士尼，大阪環球片場，秋葉原，渉谷，金國寺，大阪城<br />\n台灣 - 九份，華山文創園區，101<br />\n<br />\n大洋洲︰<br />\n<br />\n澳洲 - 悉尼歌劇院，藍山，Bondi Beach，墨爾本FLINDERS ST 車站，GREAT OCEAN ROAD，Chadstone Shopping Mall"},{"pid":"2d5e9ab341ea39c88b275ff061f0a0b2c082c27d","tid":1838612,"uid":35746,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T08:41:43.000Z","msg":"除左台灣，暫時都未重複去過"},{"pid":"53e8797f3cdf5905cc584469369aba3fa212a038","tid":1838612,"uid":130901,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T15:10:20.000Z","msg":"蚺蛇尖"},{"pid":"398e415e507b4d19e04001518e7e59f19d995038","tid":1838612,"uid":41629,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T20:42:13.000Z","msg":"土耳其 Kapadokya"},{"pid":"a4c19187157de43d5248f3cfb16963528ebdde26","tid":1838612,"uid":210165,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T20:43:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9806426588d6400631890fd2eae00afe953279d1","tid":1838612,"uid":312205,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T21:36:43.000Z","msg":"逢甲夜市"},{"pid":"4228bcd1c1728a300879d0a7fb71c971ca6a3c9d","tid":1838612,"uid":199689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4c19187157de43d5248f3cfb16963528ebdde26","tid":1838612,"uid":210165,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T20:43:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T04:48:22.000Z","msg":"海鮮市場<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b05a0f80cac7466d31575